casebody.data:
No. 09-9459. Carolyn E. O’Connor, Petitioner v. United States. 559 U.S. 1047, 130 S. Ct. 2360, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 3092.

176 L. Ed. 2d 560,

April 5, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petition for writ of certiorari before judgment to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
